{
  "stem": "3952.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He-- and he was laying in the next cot to me, and we couldn't talk him out of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The disappointment, this is what did it to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So that's the only example I can give you what disappointment-- such a disappointment can do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now, on the night-- on the 4th of May, I have a dream.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I dream with my father, and we were speaking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I said in the dream, Dad, I think that we will be liberated on the fifth day of the fifth month and the fifth hour.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he said, no, it will be the fifth day, the fifth month, but double that-- on the 10th hour.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And sure enough, 10:00 on the 5th of May, the first American soldier came into the camp, and we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So that date has a particular significance-- significance for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "When the Americans liberated us, of course, we were so hungry that we-- we went out into the neighborhood fields, and into the little town of Ebensee.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] And I will tell you something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were so weak, that we didn't speak any languages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I read and write seven languages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "At that time, I read and wrote-- I read and wrote six languages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Italian I learned after the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But when I was liberated through the Americans, I spoke only one language, the language of the hungry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I knew Herr Meister, Brot, soup, I knew those words-- Arbeit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I knew the words that were related to the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I had a friend who was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He was hospitalized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And at the hospital, they didn't feed them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So his brother said, let's go out into Ebensee, to the city and bring some fruit for Icu.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
